            "answer_text": "Bear in mind that there are many variations on the concept of \u201cbicycle\u201d. I don't expect this Snow Bike Fleet Ready to Roll! is going to win many prizes for energy efficiency. But on a hard, smooth road without too much of a headwind, this Main Line Bike Race | Lower Merion Township | Criterium style bike race (sorry about the bizarre scrolling) will be impressive, and Rose \u2013 Hulman Wins ASME Human Powered Vehicle Competition East & West should be super impressive even if there is a headwind. So, a qualified yes, bit only in terms of energy efficiency. I love to save energy, but I use a liquid fuel vehicle when I want to save time. ",
